<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #0062ff49;
            padding: 20px;
            color: white;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #2d3748;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .info-block {
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .info-block strong {
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #092045;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0052e04a;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
        }
        footer a {
            color: #021b44;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Complaint Confirmation</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{customerName}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>We have received your complaint and will investigate the issue. You can expect a response from us within 48 hours. Below are the details of your complaint for your reference:</p>

            <div class="info-block">
                <p><strong>Submission Date:</strong> {{submissionDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Complaint Summary:</strong> {{complaintSummary}}</p>
                <p><strong>Complaint Reference Number:</strong> {{complaintReferenceNumber}}</p>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="button">Contact Support</a>.</p>

            <div class="signature">
                <p>Best regards,</p>
                <p>The <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> Team</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
